In [[United States|U.S.]] [[aviation]], the [[List of aviation, aerospace and aeronautical terms|term]] '''calm wind''' is used in [[radio]] communications to describe [[wind]] that is slower than 3 knots.

2-6-5. CALM WIND CONDITIONS 
Describe the wind as calm when the wind velocity is less than three knots. 
